    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "This is a tricky one, we can do it but we need to remember people will then want to add any dom handler to it this way.\n\nWhat do you think of this:\n\n```\nsearch.addWidget(\n  instantsearch.widgets.hits({\n    container: '#hits-container',\n    onDomNodeAdded: (domNode, hitData) => {\n      // do anything you want\n    }\n  })\n);\n```\n",
