    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "From the discussions I see here, I see advanced developers (= knowing how to do DOM with either jQuery or JavaScript), willing to control the full markup generated by IS (events, html).\n\nWhat if if we said and provided you something like \"Here's a render method, please do some DOM and send it back to us\", you would be able to achieve what you want without the need to add custom API entries and without the need for the advanced users to learn those API entries, and their possible restrictions.\n",
    "created_at": "2016-06-06T09:27:09Z",
