    "body": "> Maybe we can allow the template method to return a DOM element instead of a string. That way we can bind any event with any data to hit easily. That would be really straightforward.\n\nYES! This is the ultimate \"low level\" non-leaky API that we could provide. We need to discuss this along with what are the real templating option we provide by default, will try to have a proposal soon.\n",
